This value set includes codes based on the following rules:

  • Import all the codes that are contained in http://hl7.org/fhir/ValueSet/identifier-type
  • Include all codes defined in http://hl7.org/fhir/us/davinci-pct/CodeSystem/PCTOrgIdentifierTypeCS

name: PCTOrgIdentifierTypeVS
title: PCT Organization Identifier Type Value Set
description: Codes to specify the type of identifiers for organizations to indicate usage for a specific purpose
